                            <p>The 2024 GoCardless JustGiving Awards celebrate people who fill us with inspiration, pride and hope. Nominate someone who deserves to win an award before 11th April 2024.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Latest Course -->
                <div class="sidebar_section" style="margin-left:40px">
                    <div class="sidebar_section_title">Leading philanthropist</div>
